---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="Privacy Policy | SelectStream Shop">
  <article class="legal-page">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="last-updated">Last Updated: April 9, 2026</p>

    <section>
      <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>SelectStream Shop is a minimalist curation platform. We do not require account creation or personal user data collection for browsing our stream. We may collect non-identifiable technical data such as browser type and session duration to optimize our "Quiet UI" performance.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>2. Cookies & Tracking</h2>
      <p>We use essential cookies to maintain your "Setup Builder" state in your local browser. We do not use third-party tracking pixels for behavioral advertising.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>3. Affiliate Disclosure</h2>
      <p>SelectStream is a participant in the Amazon Services LLC Associates Program, an affiliate advertising program designed to provide a means for sites to earn advertising fees by advertising and linking to Amazon.com.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>4. Data Security</h2>
      <p>We implement high-contrast security protocols to ensure your interaction with our stream is secure and private.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>5. Contact</h2>
      <p>For inquiries regarding our data practices, contact: <span class="highlight">hello@selectstreamshop.com</span></p>
    </section>
  </article>
</MainLayout>

<style>
  .legal-page {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 8rem auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #999;
  }

  h1 { font-size: 3rem; color: #fff; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  h2 { font-size: 1.2rem; color: #fff; margin-top: 3rem; letter-spacing: 0.1rem; }
  .last-updated { font-size: 0.7rem; color: #444; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.2rem; margin-bottom: 4rem; }
  section { margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .highlight { color: #fff; }
</style>
